The following changes were made to prepare the document for submission to
https://arxiv.org:

- Add the line `\pdfoutput=1` within the first five lines of the document.
- Move hyperref options out to `\hypersetup{...}` command.
- Change `backend=biber` to `backend=bibtex` in biblatex options.
- Removes commented fields from BibTeX bibliography file.
- Moves copyright information to first page.
- Removes "Work-in-progress" watermark.
